 R←Test_Misc_05(stopFlag batchFlag);⎕IO;⎕ML;⎕TRAP;parms;rc;msg;ref;filename
⍝ Send an email with a two attachments: an HTML file and a PDF file
 ⎕IO←1 ⋄ ⎕ML←1
 ⎕TRAP←(999 'C' '. ⍝ Deliberate error')(0 'N')
 R←T._Failed

 parms←⎕NS''
 parms.To←∆SERVER.Userid
 parms.CC←∆TO
 parms.Subj←'From Dyalog SMTP: ',⊃⎕SI
 parms.Body←'Simple text'
 parms.Body,←⎕UCS 13 10

 parms.Attachments←''
 filename←'./Files/APL-Code.pdf'
 parms.Attachments,←⊂filename'application/pdf'
 filename←'./Files/CrashReport.html'
 parms.Attachments,←⊂filename'text/html'

 (rc msg ref)←∆SERVER ##.SendMail parms
 Assert 0=rc

 :If ∆ConfirmEmailOkay'(check for two attachments: a PDF and an HTML file)'
     R←T._OK
 :EndIf
⍝Done
